text: Philip Cobbold (5 January 1875 - 28 December 1945) was an English cricketer. He played eighteen first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1896 and 1922. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1875 births Category:1945 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Ipswich Category:Suffolk cricketers Category:Marylebone Cricket Club cricketers Category:Gentlemen of England cricketers Category:Free Foresters cricketers
